            "id": 6076821,
            "title": "《異動股》中芯升6%華虹飆8%,半導體巨頭豪威集團擬香港上市",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社25日專訊》半導體板塊見炒作,中芯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00981:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00981\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00981-HK</a>)現價飆升6.4%,報53.45元,該股成交約1億股,涉資51.64億元;華虹(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01347:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01347\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01347-HK</a>)升7.7%,報42.05元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　近日,全球十大Fabless(無晶圓廠)半導體公司之一、影像感測器技術的先驅豪威集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:603501:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/603501\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">603501-CN</a>)遞表港交所,擬衝刺IPO。豪威集團的影像感測器已經廣泛應用於</p></section><section><p class=\"\">小米、華為等頂級手機品牌的旗艦產品中。豪威1995年在矽谷創立,僅兩年時間便推出了全球首顆單晶片彩色CIS,五年內便成功登陸納斯達克,成為全球影像感測器技術的先鋒,一度成為蘋果iPhone3GS和iPhone4的供應商。</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　根據招股書顯示,2024年豪威集團的營收及淨利分別為257.07億元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>及32.79億元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>。截至2025年7月24日,豪威集團A股報收125.79元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>,市值達1531億元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　現時,恒生指數報25380,跌287點或跌1.1%,主板成交近2140億元。國企指數報9140,跌117點或跌1.3%。恒生科技指數報5670,跌72點或跌1.3%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　即月期指新報25378,跌305點,低水2點。即月國指期貨報9138,跌126點,低水2點。即月科指期貨新報5668,跌73點,低水2點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>中芯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00981:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00981\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00981-HK</a>)</td><td>53.45元</td><td>升6.37%</td></tr><tr><td>華虹(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01347:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01347\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01347-HK</a>)</td><td>42.05元</td><td>升7.68%</td></tr><tr><td>ASMPT(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00522:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00522\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00522-HK</a>)</td><td>70.7元</td><td>升0.71%</td></tr><tr><td>上海復旦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01385:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01385\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01385-HK</a>)</td><td>29元</td><td>升5.45%</td></tr><tr><td>晶門(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02878:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02878\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02878-HK</a>)</td><td>0.47元</td><td>升4.44%</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(vs)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
